## spells.nsl 
#
## This is the spell-list for nuvie
# 
## use syntax highlighting to make this more readable (tools/nsl.vim)
#
## Reagent bitvector
# REAGENT_U6_MANDRAKE_ROOT 0x01 (  1) increase power
# REAGENT_U6_NIGHTSHADE    0x02 (  2) illusion and poison
# REAGENT_U6_BLACK_PEARL   0x04 (  4) kinetic propellent
# REAGENT_U6_BLOOD_MOSS    0x08 (  8) enhance mobility and movement
# REAGENT_U6_SPIDER_SILK   0x10 ( 16) binding
# REAGENT_U6_GARLIC        0x20 ( 32) warding and negating
# REAGENT_U6_GINSENG       0x40 ( 64) curative
# REAGENT_U6_SULFUROUS_ASH 0x80 (128) energy
#
## Syllable            Meaning     Syllable            Meaning
#  An .......... Negate/Dispel     Nox ................ Poison
#  Bet ................. Small     Ort ................. Magic
#  Corp ................ Death     Por ......... Move/Movement
#  Des ............ Lower/Down     Quas ............. Illusion
#  Ex ................ Freedom     Rel ................ Change
#  Flam ................ Flame     Sanct .. Protect/Protection
#  Grav ......... Energy/Field     Tym .................. Time
#  Hur .................. Wind     Uus .............. Raise/Up
#  In ...... Make/Create/Cause     Vas ................. Great
#  Jux ...... Danger/Trap/Harm     Wis ........ Know/Knowledge
#  Kal ......... Summon/Invoke     Xen .............. Creature
#  Lor ................. Light     Ylem ............... Matter
#  Mani ......... Life/Healing     Zu .................. Sleep
#
